parameters:
Bunny-chan: Alright, tonight the Monster Fight begins
again!! Will Shark Broccoli-sama's revenge be successful?
It's the battle that all organizations in the city are
watching♪

Spectator: Shark Broccoli-sama---!!! Please lose---!!! Suck
my dick every day---!!!

Spectator: You can keep wearing that monster suit for
another half a year!! I'll take loads of photos!!

Memimi: Hmph... Such worthless cowards, barking from the
sidelines... If I win... just you remember this later...

Cerburus Octopus: Kekeke, I've already seen through your
moves... No matter how many times you try, it's useless!!
I've got the next convenience store strategy planned out
too, look forward to it, yeah~?

Memimi: Tha... That idea... will be wasted... There's a 1000
octillion percent chance that I won't lose... Seriously...
ugh...

Bunny-chan: Okaaay, 10 seconds to start~. Please get to your
starting positions~❤︎ Good luck to both of you~❤︎

Cerburus Octopus: Kekeke, you're so slow... Too embarrassed
to make a flashy move? Take this, Octopus Piston Mach
Punch!!

Bunny-chan: The victory goes to Cerburus Octopus-san!
Congratulations❤︎ The defense was successful, and Shark
Broccoli's coup d'état has been prevented!

Cerburus Octopus: Kekekekeke, looks like I'll still have the
pleasure of your company for the new Gizagiza Mart
strategies, huh? Starting tomorrow, you're going to work so
much you'll hate it!!

Shark Broccoli was defeated and failed to take back the
organization...
